    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and usage. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in optimal shape. This is an honest, functional vehicle perfect for someone looking for affordable transportation without the expectation of a showroom finish.",
      "price": 18500.0,
