      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a dedicated project car. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and multiple engine oil leaks, meaning it is not roadworthy and will need to be towed. The exterior has noticeable rust and paint deterioration, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This is a high-effort restoration project suitable only for those with the tools and expertise to handle major mechanical overhauls.",
