    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It's been a fantastic car for me and is still in great shape, running smoothly and ready for many more adventures. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, making it a perfect pick if you want something dependable and high-quality without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by and see how nicely it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
