    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW M3 is a stunning example of a driver-focused machine, meticulously maintained and ready for its next owner. The Alpine White exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though it shows a few honest rock chips on the front fascia from spirited highway weekend drives. Inside, the Sakhir Orange leather interior is in excellent shape, free of tears or heavy bolster wear, and has never been smoked in. Mechanically, this M3 is robust; it comes with a complete service history, including a recent oil service and brake inspection. The twin-turbo inline-six pulls hard and smooth, paired with a crisp-shifting DCT transmission. All electronics, including the navigation and premium sound system, function perfectly. While there is minor curb rash on the rear passenger wheel, the Michelin Pilot Sport tires still have plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest car that balances performance with daily usability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
